耗電量！（01製圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20240808/898182684076019712609352.jpeg/vMg3Z2MGoKAGDUuTCpHUijIN1MrBUkr0ZviF32b4hd8\" alt=\"冷氣機｜7大開冷氣習慣，容易增加耗電量！（01製圖）\"><figcaption>冷氣機｜7大開冷氣習慣，容易增加耗電量！（01製圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20240808/898182686018113536630927.jpeg/o_aKRCTYpGPDR_FtyOUUaL3dC6TvE8WrVU-LAVVPiwE\" alt=\"冷氣機｜7大開冷氣習慣，容易增加耗電量！（01製圖）\"><figcaption>冷氣機｜7大開冷氣習慣，容易增加耗電量！（01製圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20240808/898182687863738368918023.jpeg/Xteba_nTwIJts2D22bww9dNW9EcSNfluc5sy1nObMtY\" alt=\"冷氣機｜7大開冷氣習慣，容易增加耗電量！（01製圖）\"><figcaption>冷氣機｜7大開冷氣習慣，容易增加耗電量！（01製圖）</figcaption></figure><p>【本文經《風傳媒》授權轉載，原文：拔插頭真的可以省電！不過3種電器插頭千萬不要拔，專家曝省電不成還容易弄壞】</p></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-03T02:35:01.986846+00:00","quality":{"score":3,"chars":2087,"images":31,"source":"HK01 熱話","fallback":"none"}}